result.execSummary:
The defendant John E Henning was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. John E Henning is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • John E Henning was found guilty of Child Enticement-Sexual Contact, a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.07(1).
